parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of Duro tires can cause tire blowouts, loss of control, and accidents, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Dry rotting of tires
fractures in the side wall of tires
tires splitting in the treads
uneven wear
cupping.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty spare tire mount can cause the spare tire to become dislodged while driving, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Spare tire holder fails at welds
spare tire becomes loose or falls off
spare tire mount breaks or cracks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaks in the camper can cause water damage, mold, and electrical issues, which can lead to safety hazards and costly repairs.
symptoms: Water leaks in the camper
improper installation of drain holes
water damage
mold growth.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An overheating heating system can cause burns, fires, or other safety hazards, especially if it is not properly vented or maintained.
symptoms: Excessive heat
blisters on skin
heat does not distribute evenly
improper installation or maintenance of heating system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake wires can cause the brakes to fail, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brakes are extremely loud when applied
the brakes fail to engage
the brake wires are pinched or damaged by the dump valve shafts
the brake wires are loose and not secured.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tires can cause a loss of control, leading to accidents and potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The tires blow out while driving
the tires are damaged due to excessive weight or load.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design of the hitch pin box can cause the trailer to disconnect from the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential rollovers, which can result in severe injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The trailer becomes disconnected from the vehicle while in motion
loss of control
swaying or fishtailing of the trailer
rollover of the vehicle and/or trailer.
